snippet.title: Egging On - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description: Learn all about your hazardous climb and check out gameplay in this latest trailer for Egging On, an upcoming game where you star as an egg trying to make your way to freedom. The trailer gives us a look at physics-based egg rolling movement mechanics, the dangers of falling, and much more. Egging On will be available on PC.
